321
00:20:13,870 --> 00:20:16,070
♪ Pengakuan ♪

322
00:20:17,890 --> 00:20:22,689
♪ Bisakah mengatakan
apa yang ingin dikatakan padaku? ♪

323
00:20:22,690 --> 00:20:26,000
♪ Membiarkan keinginan mekar
seperti bunga sakura ♪

324
00:20:26,030 --> 00:20:27,190
♪ Hati yang melayang ♪

325
00:20:27,270 --> 00:20:31,150
♪ Sedikit panik, rasa tidak berdaya
