327
00:20:35,620 --> 00:20:39,650
♪ Bisakah memberitahuku
jawaban yang dinantikan ♪

328
00:20:39,740 --> 00:20:42,940
♪ Kamu sengaja curang saat menatapku ♪

329
00:20:43,050 --> 00:20:44,370
♪ Seperti anak kecil ♪

330
00:20:44,390 --> 00:20:48,360
♪ Langit berbintang bersinar
